    <a href="/pet-vaccinations-lake-in-the-hills-il/">customized vaccination protocols</a>,
    <a href="/dental-care/">dental care with digital radiography</a>,
    <a href="/surgery/">surgery</a>,
    <a href="/spay-neuter-lake-in-the-hills-il/">spay and neuter</a>,
    <a href="/senior-pet-care-lake-in-the-hills-il/">senior pet care</a>,
    <a href="/pet-allergy-treatment-lake-in-the-hills-il/">allergy treatment</a>,
    <a href="/laboratory-diagnostics/">in-house laboratory diagnostics</a>, and
    <a href="/emergency-urgent-care/">same-day urgent care</a> during business hours.
  </p>
  <p>
    Because we are privately owned by Dr. Burgess, every service recommendation is based on
    clinical judgment rather than corporate revenue goals. We will never suggest a procedure your
    pet does not need, and we will always explain why we believe a recommended course of action is
    warranted. Crystal Lake residents who have grown wary of upselling at corporate-backed clinics
    often tell us this transparency is what initially drew them in — and what keeps them coming
    back.
  </p>
